            title="Required">

<a href="#cidrblock_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Cidr<wbr>Block</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}CIDR block for the VPC
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="createadditionalprivatesubnets_csharp">
<a href="#createadditionalprivatesubnets_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Create<wbr>Additional<wbr>Private<wbr>Subnets</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Set to `true` to create a network ACL protected subnet in each Availability Zone. If `false`, the CIDR parameters for those subnets will be ignored.
If `true`, it also requires that the 'Create private subnets' parameter is also `true` to have any effect.
Default is `true`
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="createflowlogs_csharp">
<a href="#createflowlogs_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Create<wbr>Flow<wbr>Logs</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Enable Flow Logs to capture IP traffic for the VPC. Defaults to `true`
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="createnatgateways_csharp">
<a href="#createnatgateways_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Create<wbr>Nat<wbr>Gateways</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Set to `false` when creating only private subnets. If `true`, both CreatePublicSubnets and CreatePrivateSubnets must also be `true`.
Default is `true`
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="createprivatesubnets_csharp">
<a href="#createprivatesubnets_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Create<wbr>Private<wbr>Subnets</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Set to `false` to create only public subnets. If `false`, the CIDR parameters for ALL private subnets will be ignored.
Default is `true`.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="createpublicsubnets_csharp">
<a href="#createpublicsubnets_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Create<wbr>Public<wbr>Subnets</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>

{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">

<a href="#enablednshostnames_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Enable<wbr>Dns<wbr>Hostnames</a>

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">bool</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}A boolean flag to enable/disable DNS support in the VPC. Defaults true.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="flowlogslogformat_csharp">
<a href="#flowlogslogformat_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Flow<wbr>Logs<wbr>Log<wbr>Format</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The fields to include in the flow log record, in the order in which they should appear. Specify the fields using the ${field-id} format,

{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="flowlogsmaxaggregationinterval_csharp">
<a href="#flowlogsmaxaggregationinterval_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Flow<wbr>Logs<wbr>Max<wbr>Aggregation<wbr>Interval</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">double</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The maximum interval of time during which a flow of packets is captured and aggregated into a flow log record. You can specify 60 seconds
(1 minute) or 600 seconds (10 minutes). Default is `600`
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="flowlogsretentionperiodindays_csharp">

</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">double</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}Number of days to retain the VPC Flow Logs in CloudWatch. Defaults to `14`.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="flowlogstraffictype_csharp">
<a href="#flowlogstraffictype_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Flow<wbr>Logs<wbr>Traffic<wbr>Type</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>{{% md %}}The type of traffic to log. You can log traffic that the resource accepts or rejects, or all traffic.
Default is `REJECT`.
{{% /md %}}</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="instancetenancy_csharp">
<a href="#instancetenancy_csharp" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">Instance<wbr>Tenancy</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">string</span>
    </dt>
